»CL0:Rackler & Doc Holiday/ex. Lego are
planning to release an EP in the near
future. After leaving the active Amiga
scene they formed 'YAKITORIH', an
elektronik soundproject, and won the
1st place at the 'Up'n'Away
Musicsearch' at the PopKomm '96 with
one of their modules. Contact Rackler
under <rackler@wtal.de> and watch out
for the sooncoming releases from
YAKITORIH!
